Spokane_Valley.KKZX: KKZX (98.9 FM) is a classic rock radio station serving the Spokane, Washington, area. The station offers up a steady diet of rock music hits from the 1960s to the early 1990s, along with colorful personalities such as Jim Arnold, Laura Hall and Jason McCollim. The station is an affiliate of The Beatle Years, Acoustic Storm, Nights with Alice Cooper, Time Warp and Nikki Sixx's Sixx Sense.
